<toc>
 
<!-- added this section name -->
<sect> Information for W32 Chipset Users <p>

<tt>XF86_W32</tt> has been discontinued as of XFree86-4.0, since all of its
functions (and more) are now included in the SVGA server <tt>XF86_SVGA</tt>.
All necessary information on using Tseng chips with <tt>XF86_SVGA</tt> is
provided in <tt>README.tseng</tt>




